dct_description_sm: issued Jan. 1889 F.M. Thorn Superintendant, varified: B.A. Colonna, Assistant in charge of office.
Depths shown by soundings in feet.

Triangulation by C.P. Bolles and A. Boschke. Topography by H.L. Whiting, A.W. Longfellow, C.M. Bache, and A.S. Wadsworth. Hydrography by J.N. Maffit, C.R.P. Rodgers and W.I. Vinal. Varification of hydrography by W.H. Brownson.
Includes notes on tides, buoys, and shifting sands.
